---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Snake minimalist Game - Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for Snake minimalist Game, detailing data handling practices for the Google Play Store release."
>
  <article class="min-h-screen py-16 space-y-8">
    <header class="space-y-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#0f1a20]">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-700">Last updated: 22 October 2025</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Snake minimalist Game respects your privacy and is committed to protecting any information that may
        be collected while using the app. This policy explains how information is handled inside the game.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#5bc0be]">1. Information we collect</h2>
      <p>
        Snake minimalist Game does not collect, store, or share personal information from users. The game does
        not request registration, name, email, or any other identifiable data.
      </p>
      <p>
        If third-party services are used (such as Google Play Games, AdMob, or others), those services may
        collect data according to their own privacy policies.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#5bc0be]">2. Use of information</h2>
      <p>
        If non-personal information is collected (for example, anonymous statistics or performance data), it
        will only be used to:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Improve the gameplay experience.</li>
        <li>Analyze bugs or technical issues.</li>
        <li>Optimize the overall performance of the app.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#5bc0be]">3. Cookies and similar technologies</h2>
      <p>
        Snake minimalist Game does not use cookies directly. However, external services (such as analytics or
        advertising providers) may use cookies or anonymous identifiers in line with their own policies.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#5bc0be]">4. Third-party links</h2>
      <p>
        The app may include links or integrations with external services. Once you access those links, Snake
        minimalist Game has no control over their content or policies, so you should review their respective
        privacy statements.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#5bc0be]">5. Security</h2>
      <p>
        We are committed to keeping the app as secure as possible. Even though personal information is not
        handled, we apply good security practices to prevent unauthorized access or issues that may affect the
        user experience.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#5bc0be]">6. Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>
        This Privacy Policy may be updated at any time. Please review it periodically. Any modifications will be
        published on this page or within the app.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#5bc0be]">7. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at
        <a class="text-[#f42c04] font-medium" href="mailto:andy.c.chipol@gmail.com">andy.c.chipol@gmail.com</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <footer class="pt-6 text-sm text-gray-500">
      <p>Thank you for playing Snake minimalist Game.</p>
    </footer>
  </article>
</Layout>

